data.description: Price reduction! Sellers are willing to entertain a 2/1 temporary buy-down option or closing cost contribution. Hometown Heroes might apply. This nicely updated and well-maintained home, situated on a corner lot in a quiet neighborhood offers comfort and practicality. This home provides convenience and tranquility with a one-car, attached garage, and a privacy fence. Inside you will discover a spacious living area, filled with natural light and a modern kitchen, thoughtfully updated to meet your daily needs. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living and dining areas, creating a versatile gathering space. This home also boasts a brand-new air conditioning unit to keep you cool on those hot summer days. Whether you enjoy your morning coffee on the back porch, tending to the yard, or hosting a small gathering this home offers a practical and comfortable lifestyle. Updates on this home include but are not limited to a new water heater with leak detection and wifi, remodeled bathrooms and kitchen, a built-in wine refrigerator, quartz countertops in the kitchen, granite countertops in both bathrooms, recessed lighting throughout, crown molding, matching ceramic tile throughout the house, updated windows and doors, matching stainless steel appliances, white PVC privacy fence with double gate, new energy-efficient A/C unit. Ask us about this home's interest rate buy-down options and downpayment assistance programs.
